	<h1>Castiglione del Lago: Essentials &amp; Sights</h1>

<section class="heroCard">
	<div class="introGrid">
		<div>
			<p>
				Welcome to Castiglione del Lago, a charming walled hill town on the shores of Lake Trasimeno. Once a strategic stronghold between Umbria and Tuscany, it later flourished under the della Corgna family in the 1500s—leaving behind a beautiful old town, fortress walls and Renaissance palace rooms to explore.
			</p>

			<p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
				This page highlights some of the best essentials and sights in Castiglione del Lago—perfect for an easy stroll, a relaxed lakeside afternoon, or a simple “what should we do today?” plan.
			</p>
		</div>

		<img
			src="/photos/castiglione.jpeg"
			alt="Castiglione del Lago"
			loading="lazy"
		/>
	</div>
</section>

	
	<div class="callout">
		<h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Essentials at a glance</h2>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Best supermarkets:</strong> COOP &amp; Gala Superstore</li>
			<li><strong>Best laundry:</strong> Lava Piu (24‑hour self service)</li>
			<li><strong>Best pharmacy:</strong> Farmacia Nafissi SRL</li>
